<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;953.6 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Technical assistance. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
On an annual basis, each field office will provide technical assistance to eligible applicants for these purposes:

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(a) To provide eligible applicants with information on how to apply for funds and how grants will be selected and awarded;
and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) To inform eligible applicants of changes in the program. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

